Today <a href="http://dushonok.com/2013/02/12/veggies-of-the-week-from-lufa-farm/">the basket of the week from LufaFarm</a> includes: tomatoes, lettuce, swiss chard, bean sprouts, potatoes, onions, cucumbers, and a bouquet of kale. Lots of greens, and it is very good for fresh spring salads!

